metadata.name: This is a crisis
metadata.description:
My mind is falling apart.
My soul wants freedom.
My soul is revolting.
I don’t care anymore.
I want to be free.

I am missing *the* critical piece of the puzzle.
The missing link of the alphabet.
I hear noises but I struggle to understand their meaning.
And me pretending to know doesn’t work anymore.

The honest answer is that I don’t know.
Or I cannot know.
Or the time has not yet come for me to know.

I am scared.
Of dishonesty.
Of losing control.
